Global Conventional Electric Hand Dryers Market Insights
Conventional Electric Hand Dryers Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.9 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Conventional Electric Hand Dryers Market Overview
The global conventional electric hand dryers market was valued at approximately USD 1.5 billion in 2024, and it is projected to grow at a CAGR of 5.2% during the forecast period (2025-2030). This steady growth is driven by increasing hygiene awareness, eco-friendly initiatives, and the ongoing demand for cost-effective, efficient alternatives to paper towels. The market is expanding due to innovations in dryer technology, better energy efficiency, and growing adoption in public washrooms, airports, commercial spaces, and industrial facilities. Key regional markets include North America, Europe, and the Asia Pacific, with emerging demand in developing regions.

